<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 11.75pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:
9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F4E79">Under the Passenger Sales
Agency Rules, all IATA Accredited Agencies must ensure its full compliance with
the PCI DSS.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<u1:p></u1:p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 11.75pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:
9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F4E79">&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: 11.75pt; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size:
9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F4E79">The PCI DSS, is a global
standard aimed at helping merchants (Agency) understand and implement standards
for security policies, technologies and ongoing processes that protect their
payment systems from breaches and theft of cardholder data.</span><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<u1:p></u1:p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:
11.75pt"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;
